dct_description_sm: A compilation of data and imagery of the Monterey Bay and the adjacent seafloor, including coastline, imagery, and bathymetry.
"Compiled by the Monterey Bay Aquarium Research Institute Mapping Team"--Inside of container.

System requirements: Computer; web browser; text editor or word-processing program; image-display software capable of opening TIFF images of 5 MB; ISO 9660-compatible CD drive; computer display supporting 256 or more colors.  Recommended software: ArcView GIS with Spatial Analyst Extension, ARC/INFO, or ArcExplorer (the latter included on the disc, requires Windows98/2000 or Windows NT 4.0 and at least 13 MB hard disk space).
